{"tid":1831581,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候幫党铁檢查下修復進度","createTime":"2020-01-20T13:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T14:13:18.000Z","uid":301882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85000760cd69f803e7a2e66c7f3757e6072ff7c1","tid":1831581,"uid":301882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"党铁作為Xiang Gang Ren既大眾運輸公司<br />\n每日都仲有大量設施聲稱被破壞<br />\n用各種核突嘅方法遮蓋<br />\n而党铁又冇足夠既人手同零件修理<br />\n冇辦法重新投入服務<br />\n令市民諸多不便<br />\n<br />\n然而<br />\n咁多機壞<br />\n但係又咁啱有齊每樣一部可以服務<br />\n修復進度令人擔憂<br />\n<br />\n既然党铁咁慘唔夠人手檢查同修理<br />\n我哋作為手執一手既党铁老闆<br />\n就等我哋嚟幫佢檢查<br />\n提高公司嘅透明度<br />\n為公司重建關公形象出一分力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劇本: <br />\n1. 開live或錄影<br />\n<br />\n2. 證明當刻日期時間 (例如影低著咗網路自動調正功能既電話時間畫面, 或者直頭問党铁職員幾號幾點)<br />\n<br />\n3. 前往目標設施, 幫佢撕開膠紙封條檢查傷勢 (一個人勉強嘅, 記住搵可靠嘅朋友幫手)<br />\n<br />\n4. zoom in影下各個細部, 欣賞唔同嘅角度, 介紹下佢完美無裂既mon, 或者冇通電既機身<br />\n<br />\n5. 安然離開, 或者向職員查詢設施修復情況, 幾時會整好, 會唔會係唔記得開電制etc.<br />\n再唔係訪問下現場乘客, 了解下設施停用對佢哋既影響, 會否好唔方便<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大中指: 見機行事, 零損兵<br />\n<br />\n以上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n党铁　堅係送你一程"},{"pid":"0c737040a2359c61987656e5543738742fa7aaf6","tid":1831581,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"GOOD IDEA<br />\n<br />\n你做完之後報告返個進度<br />\n<br />\n支持你"},{"pid":"fca36c4b9948fe05025b8c5eb6145d31768329cf","tid":1831581,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:16:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1.22荔枝角收押所<br />\n1.24荔枝角收押所<br />\n1.27和你shop 彩虹戰衣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyA7Vuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyA7Vuq.jpg&h=3f02ab45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSBSm9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSBSm9r.jpg&h=fac8cfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HMKXHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HMKXHM.png&h=a3a1e633&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaZD19s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaZD19s.jpg&h=065725f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*不要屌狗 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多聲援出庭手足</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVq0v20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVq0v20.jpg&h=524f4eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加入工會<br />\ntg: hkonstrike<br />\nFB: 二百萬三罷聯合戰線<br />\n‼️連儂廁<br />\n‼️Twitter戰線"},{"pid":"39bef09ebf2d9a3c18149a8a9209f9391edce1ec","tid":1831581,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"我樓下個站<br />\nD單程票機過左幾個月都仲係扮壞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要整既兩個星期都搞掂啦"}]}